dct_description_sm: Includes metro map, map of "Barrio Gótico" and tourist information. Some buildings and historical landmarks are shown pictorially. Ancillary maps on verso: Ciutat Vella -- Gothic Quarter - Barceloneta -- Barrio Gotico -- Barcelona Metro lines. Includes indices of places of interest, tourist information, and color photographs.
